file_content.text: Mayday! Mayday! Can anyone read me?
Comm's blocked. That blasted satellite! Wasn't enough to shoot me down....
The Empire's on the ground already. They'll search the ship, find the intel....
I'm blasting the intel out with the garbage. That ought to keep the Imperials busy.
The intel's away! I'm going down--
[The decrypter has activated a recorded distress call from the dead SIS agent.]
[There is a recording on this SIS agent's body, but the message is garbled and unintelligible.]
[This data recorder seems to have come from Agent Jago's ship. The decrypter activates a recorded distress call.]
[The distress call ends abruptly. There is nothing you can do for Agent Jago, but his intel may still be in the area.]
[This data recorder seems to have come from the crashed ship nearby. It cannot be activated at this time.]
